channel.title: Status checker not accepting my server
channel.description: Well, I recently figured out how to set up my No-IP, and I can log on with the No-IP address, and I'm on the server when I put the server up on the list, but it keeps on saying my server is offline. Can someone go onto twilightzone.servegame.com and tell me if it works, or can you help me fix this problem?
